Sure, here are some brand name ideas based on the words mentioned above:

1. NutriMate
2. EffortEase
3. StreamKit
4. SustainWise
5. CareCompanion
6. FitFamPro
7. PureEaseful
8. HappyPrepCo

These brand names aim to incorporate the ideas of nutrition, ease, sustainability, caring, fitness, wholesomeness, and happiness into memorable and easy-to-pronounce brand names. Remember to conduct a trademark search and market research before choosing a brand name for your business, and make sure the name is relevant to your target audience and the products you offer.
